                  <ce:simple-para id="sp0095" view="all">Biomass measurements were taken in 2012–13 and 2020–21. Litter and Soil measurements were only taken in 2020–21 <ce:sup loc="post">+</ce:sup>.</ce:simple-para>
                  <ce:simple-para id="sp0100" view="all">C values are in Mg ha<ce:sup loc="post">−1</ce:sup>, C:N is a unitless ratio, and net soil fraction, “netF (%)”, is the percent of soil from the entire soil sample found in that soil fraction. QULO = <ce:italic>Q. lobata</ce:italic>, FRLA = <ce:italic>F. latifolia</ce:italic>, POFR = <ce:italic>P. fremontii</ce:italic>, SAGO = <ce:italic>S. gooddingii.</ce:italic>
                  </ce:simple-para>
